OL,3,CWhat will a new Prime Minister mean
OL,4,Cfor the region?
OL,6,FYou can see the latest edition of
OL,7,FAround The House here:
OL,9,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,10,Fis joined by Emma Lewell MP (Labour),
OL,11,FDavid Mundell MP (Con), and Tom Gordon
OL,12,F(Lib Dem) on Wednesday 8 July 2026.
OL,14,FOur new Prime Minister will enter
OL,15,FDowning Street later this month,
OL,16,Ffollowing Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,17,Fresignation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
