OL,3,CWhat will a new Prime Minister mean
OL,4,Cfor the region?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham is poised to take charge,
OL,7,Fpromising greater devolution, a new
OL,8,FNumber 10 North and "good growth in
OL,9,Fevery British post code."
OL,11,FThe change of power at the top of
OL,12,Fgovernment will affect us all, as the
OL,13,Fnew PM tries to make rapid progress to
OL,14,Fbring about his vision.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
