OL,3,CWhat will a new Prime Minister mean
OL,4,Cfor the region?
OL,6,FTom Sheldrick's panel consider how it
OL,7,Fmight affect the cost of living and
OL,8,Fthe role of elected Mayors, who are
OL,9,Fbeing promised wider powers. One of
OL,10,Fthe challenges facing Andy Burnham
OL,11,Fwill be finding nearly #5bn to fill a
OL,12,Fhole in the nearly #300bn plans for
OL,13,Fthe long-awaited Defence Investment
OL,14,FPlan.
OL,16,FIt promises to boost British industry
OL,17,Fand skills - and MPs in our region are
OL,18,Fcampaigning for contracts to be placed
OL,19,Fhere.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
